title: Séura Storm: Outdoor Televisions for Shaded Locations
description:
Imagine a TV that lets you escape from the indoors. With a Séura Outdoor TV, you can bring your family and friends together for a movie outside.

Enjoy reliable weatherproof performance built to withstand the extremes of Mother Nature. Only Séura Outdoor TVs have a Triple Lock Seal to protect against the elements and anti-glare glass to ensure the best viewing experience. 

The Séura Storm Outdoor TV was voted Best New Product of 2015 by CEDIA, the leading authority in home technology.

Reimagine your backyard with Séura.
